# Recruit interview participants for your portfolio project

Interview goals: 

I want to understand common challenges found by food-truck owners and employees when making their food menus available to client and identify the opportunity to improve their experience and their clients'

## Interview questions: 

Are customers able to see the menu while they wait in line?
Is your menu updated based on availability of items or is it static?
What challenges are there currently in the ordering process for you and for your clients?
What would you need to address these challenges?

## Target participant characteristics:

Food-truck owners and employees
Have been in business for at least 12 months
Include participants of different genders and age groups

